---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";

---

<BaseLayout title = "About Me" sideBarActiveItemID="aboutme">
    <div>
      <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">About Me</div>
    </div>

    

    <div class="py-2 text-lg space-y-3 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
        I am a mechatronics engineering student in my final year from the University of British Columbia (UBC) with a focus on embedded systems.
        My interest in engineering started in highschool where I grew a passion for math and physics due to incredible teachers who made me passionate about STEM.
        I chose engineering because I like to see direct impact of my work, and I want to contribute to building innovative products that make a difference in people's lives.
        Over the last few years, I've gained 2 years of valuable work experience, from small fast-paced startup environments to working in big tech. In all my work,
        I take ownership of my projects and create an impact with my work while growing my skills. 
        </p>

        <p>
        In my most recent internship at Bosch in Germany, I worked as an embedded systems engineer where I conducted R&D to drive advancements in diagnostic
        capabilities for biomedical applications. In my role before that, I made significant contributions to the successful first launch of an early stage startup in a
        fast paced environment.
        </p>

        <p>
        In the time I was not at internships, I was actively involved with the Aerospace club on campus for a few years, leading the software team and competing in
        national competitions where I contributed to achieving 2nd place with an innovation award.
        </p>

      <p>
        Outside of academics, I enjoy going to the gym and staying active. I've curious about how things work, which often leads me to explore topics beyond
        my coursework. I have a strong passion for engineering and I am always eager to learn and grow in my field. I am excited about the future and the opportunities that lie ahead as I continue to pursue my career
        in the embedded systems space. Some specific industries that I am interested in include aerospace, robotics, and biomedical.
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>


  

  <div class="mt-8">
    <div class="text-2xl w-full font-bold mb-4">Skills</div>
    <div class="text-base space-y-2">
      <p><strong>Firmware & Hardware:</strong> C, C++, STM32, ARM Cortex-M MCUs, RTOS, FreeRTOS, I2C, SPI, CAN, UART, Oscilloscope, Logic Analyzer, DMM, SWD, LTspice, Altium Designer, KiCad, Board Bring-up & Validation, Soldering</p>
      <p><strong>Software:</strong> Python (NumPy, Pandas, CircuitPython), MATLAB, Simulink, Docker, Git & GitHub, Linux CLI, ROS2</p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline ml-0">Contact</a>
    <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">Projects</a>
    <a href="/capstone_reflection" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">Capstone Reflection</a>
    <a href="/Shivam_Kataria_Resume.pdf" class="btn btn-outline ml-5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resume</a>
  </div>




</BaseLayout>